text: Michela Este (born 27 April 1985) is an Italian rugby union player. She was a member of the Italian national rugby team. She participated at the 2009 Women's Six Nations Championship, and 2017 Women's Rugby World Cup. She played for Benetton Rugby Treviso. == References == Category:1985 births Category:Italian rugby union players Category:Living people
